game.name: Duck Carnival Shoot
game.description:
May be you like the ducks in a way as we do. It is amazing to spend some time with these cute birds. Are you ready to accept this unique challenge where duck hunting will be your primary job? Join Duck Carnival Shoot game and get you prepared in the ultimate shooting combat! Your objective in this brand new action game is to take aim and shoot the ducks before the clock turns off. Do not forget to earn coins that you can use to upgrade your accuracy at its best!

Try to earn more coins to complete all mini missions perfectly! We are damn sure that you will be surprised by the environment where ducks are available in a great number. They will keep coming from the both sides of the screen. No need to show sympathy on them and shoot all ducks in business suits! It is your responsibility to gun down mafia duck boss to grab extra points. This cool html5 gun shooter features fun and challenging gameplay. 

Remember you will get penalized heavily in case of shooting the bombs. Your game will reach to an end if the time runs out. You will see the ducks moving or static. However, you need to aim your target using the mouse and shoot down them perfectly. Ensure your victory by putting your precision and reflex to test! Good luck to score a big score and make you feel proud by becoming the best shooter of your area! Keep checking out more new shooting games on atmegame.com to have more fun and entertainment!
